snippet.title: Blood Rush - Official Demo release teaser
snippet.description:
Blood Rush is an upcoming skill based roguelite FPS designed to be an intense experience. Upgrade yourself, get new abilities, get new guns, upgrade them and find synergies to destroy anyone or anything standing on your way to escape a Dante inspired Hell!

Check the game out on Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2435870/Blood_Rush/
Epic Game Store : https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/blood-rush-c905c8

More to come soon !

Teaser music :
Fuzzeke - Pistol Loader
